{"tid":373113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【澳門直擊】市民摸黑上街沖涼 唔靠政府自發派水互助","createTime":"2017-08-24T18:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T03:51:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43d4c567947d47ac084d32b400910cf659d6d34a","tid":373113,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T18:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170824/large/1503581970_02ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170824%2Flarge%2F1503581970_02ed.jpg&h=aac21e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天鴿肆虐澳門過後，當地多條街道佈滿垃圾，街邊的垃圾被雨水弄濕，傳出陣陣臭味，更有不少烏蠅、蚊子滋生，衞生情況惡劣。災無情，人間有愛，市民埋怨政府無能之餘，有自願上街清理的市民表示，衞生情況嚴重，加上水資源缺乏，且澳門天色已轉晴，溫度上升，「如果政府再唔清d垃圾，令細菌滋生，擔心會出事」。澳門市民聯合會更準備了約2500支樽裝水免費派發予市民。<br />\n<br />\n入夜後，部分地方供電仍未恢復，市民要摸黑煮食，甚至走到街上，在街燈照明下，着住衫露天沖涼。<br />\n澳門政府晚上表示，為解決居民用水困難，海關開放三個自來水供水點予市民使用，分別為媽閣海關總部、青州海關大樓、海島海關巡邏站（路環碼頭），有需要市民可前往上址取水。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170824/57123579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170824%2F57123579&d=5s5Li%2B1jkSbDAsI3L%2BpAV54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d10f2e10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170824%2F57123579&h=70c669a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170824/57123579</a>"},{"pid":"a2deb9084ec30c20699f331c38d8cb0305e46a23","tid":373113,"uid":7840,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fb3a8ffc16b5d4468a5c240e1eb8ad09d78afbd","tid":373113,"uid":14250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T20:08:00.000Z","msg":"手持樽裝水"},{"pid":"2f3d833786e0ff03580b92f17ace51eb0ff00aca","tid":373113,"uid":6778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T20:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"